<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10617371>
    dc:description "Figs 32−36. Loxosceles bodoquena Bertani & Gallão sp. nov. 32–35. Holotype, ♀ (LES 0028828). 32. Carapace. 33. Left palp, dorsal view. 34−35. Spermathecae. 34. Ventral view. 35. Dorsal view, bursa copulatrix unfolded below. 36. Paratype, ♀ (LES 0028831), spermathecae, ventral view. Abbreviations: bc = bursa copulatrix; r = receptacle; tp = transverse sclerotized plate. Scale bars: 32−33 = 1 mm; 34−36 = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10617371/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10617373>
    dc:description "Figs 37−43. Loxosceles bodoquena Bertani & Gallão sp. nov., paratype, ♂ (LES 0028829). 37. Carapace. 38−40. Left palp bulb. 38. Dorsal view. 39. Prolateral view. 40. Retrolateral view. 41−43. Left palp. 41. Retrolateral view. 42. Prolateral view. 43. Dorsal view. Scale bars: 37, 41−43 = 1 mm; 38−40 = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10617373/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10617377>
    dc:description "Figs 44−47. Loxosceles bodoquena Bertani & Gallão sp. nov., in the wild. 44. Female. 45. Male. 46−47. Dente de Cão cave, general view." ;
